## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Overview stats query actual database counts
- [ ] Severity distribution sums to total blocks
- [ ] Top rules ordered by block count descending
- [ ] Pack stats include percentage and top rules
- [ ] Agent stats track which agents trigger most blocks
- [ ] Time series data works for hourly and daily periods
- [ ] Quick stats endpoint returns in <100ms
- [ ] Trend calculations accurate vs previous periods
- [ ] All unit tests pass with comprehensive logging
- [ ] All integration tests pass
- [ ] All E2E tests pass

## Performance Considerations

- Consider caching stats with short TTL (10-30 seconds)
- Use database indexes for time-range queries
- Quick stats endpoint should be fast for dashboard polling
- Consider materialized views for complex aggregations
